Class SubSchemaModificationWrapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.forgerock.openam.upgrade.SubSchemaModificationWrapper

  • public class SubSchemaModificationWrapper
extends Object
    Wrapper class that contains the modifications within a subschema; currently only new sub schema are supported.
    Author:
    Steve Ferris
